item.description: We have been invited to set up a booth discussing Rotaract and community service opportunities with local high school students. We can discuss opportunities to join Interact clubs during high school, or getting involved with Rotaract as they move on to college. Possible activities include writing thanksgiving greeting cards for active service members, veterans, etc… Contact: Eric at President@bostonrotaract.org
